::Army-Dillo::

Army Dillo looks toward earth from his stasis pod.  He
would land there any second now.  He thought to
himself "Were will I go and what will I do."  He knew
he must find the maximals but how could he find them?

A couple minutes later he crash landed on earth and
got out of the stasis pod.  Now he had to find the maximals.
